flowchart LR
    KEY[Cryptographic Key]

    KEY --> GEN[generate: HSM / KMS]
    GEN --> ACTIVE[active: sign / encrypt]
    ACTIVE --> ROTATE[rotation trigger]
    ROTATE --> NEWKEY[new active key]
    ROTATE --> GRACE[old key: verify-only grace period]
    GRACE --> RETIRE[retire old key]
    RETIRE --> ARCHIVE[archive / destroy]

    ACTIVE --> USE[encrypt payload or sign webhook]
    USE --> VERIFY[recipient: verify / decrypt]
